            "topic": "SX-SJ",
            "difficulty": "中等",
            "stem": "在△ABC中，内角A,B,C的对边分别为a,b,c，已知a=3，c=2，B=60°。\n（1）求b的值；\n（2）求sinA的值。",
            "solution": {
                "steps": [
                    "（1）由余弦定理：b²=a²+c²-2accosB",
                    "代入：b²=3²+2²-2×3×2×cos60°=9+4-12×1/2=13-6=7",
                    "所以b=√7",
                    "（2）由正弦定理：a/sinA = b/sinB",
                    "代入：3/sinA = √7/sin60° = √7/(√3/2) = 2√7/√3",
                    "所以sinA = 3 × (√3/(2√7)) = (3√3)/(2√7) = (3√21)/14"
                ],
                "modelResponse": "（1）b=√7\n（2）sinA=(3√21)/14",
                "finalAnswer": "（1）√7 （2）(3√21)/14"
            },
