            "difficulty": "较难",
            "stem": "已知数列{an}满足a1=1，a_{n+1}=2a_n+1。\n（1）求数列{an}的通项公式；\n（2）求数列{an}的前n项和Sn。",
            "solution": {
                "steps": [
                    "（1）由a_{n+1}=2a_n+1，两边加1得：a_{n+1}+1=2(a_n+1)\n   令b_n=a_n+1，则b_1=a_1+1=2，且b_{n+1}=2b_n\n   所以{b_n}是首项为2，公比为2的等比数列\n   b_n=2·2^(n-1)=2^n\n   因此a_n=b_n-1=2^n-1",
                    "（2）Sn=∑(2^k-1)=∑2^k - ∑1 = (2+2²+...+2^n) - n\n   前n项和：2+2²+...+2^n = 2(2^n-1)/(2-1)=2^(n+1)-2\n   所以Sn=2^(n+1)-2-n"
                ],
                "modelResponse": "（1）a_n=2^n-1\n（2）Sn=2^(n+1)-n-2",
                "finalAnswer": "（1）2^n-1 （2）2^(n+1)-n-2"
            },
